---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="How Australian Home Collective handles affiliate links."
>
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Disclosure</p>
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Some links on Australian Home Collective may be affiliate links. If you use them, we
        may receive a commission at no extra cost to you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="content narrow">
    <p>
      If you use an affiliate link, Australian Home Collective may receive a commission from
      the partner website. We aim to make this clear while keeping guides focused on reader
      usefulness.
    </p>
    <h2>How we keep guides useful</h2>
    <p>
      A commission does not guarantee that something will be included. We may mention a product,
      brand or category because it helps explain a decision, comparison or practical
      consideration.
    </p>
    <h2>Reader choice</h2>
    <p>
      You are never required to use our links. We encourage readers to check current
      availability, policies and suitability directly with the relevant website before making
      a decision.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
